{"tid":2068852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[ 支那又跪了 ]  中共和挪威當局均認為三文魚非病毒來源","createTime":"2020-06-18T03:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T04:34:18.000Z","uid":21470,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"33f6b3b776736efe8fa4559baa9fbb7fd33acb67","tid":2068852,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:44:38.000Z","msg":"中國和挪威當局均認為三文魚非病毒來源<br />\n18.06.2020 11:06<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，中方和挪威當局都認為，挪威三文魚並非北京新發地批發市場的新型冠狀病毒來源。<br />\n<br />\n北京當局在市場內切割三文魚的砧板上檢測出病毒，雖然挪威食品安全部門早前已指，無證據顯示魚類能夠感染新型冠狀病毒，但挪威三文魚商戶表示，有中國企業取消訂單。中國早前亦暫停歐洲三文魚進口，北京多間超市把三文魚下架。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1312852&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1312852%26csid%3D261_367&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4watywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=4c5146bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1312852&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"3c9ecf55183e36613e72742afda22953fa294e6f","tid":2068852,"uid":7343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"33f6b3b776736efe8fa4559baa9fbb7fd33acb67","tid":2068852,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:44:38.000Z","msg":"中國和挪威當局均認為三文魚非病毒來源<br />\n18.06.2020 11:06<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，中方和挪威當局都認為，挪威三文魚並非北京新發地批發市場的新型冠狀病毒來源。<br />\n<br />\n北京當局在市場內切割三文魚的砧板上檢測出病毒，雖然挪威食品安全部門早前已指，無證據顯示魚類能夠感染新型冠狀病毒，但挪威三文魚商戶表示，有中國企業取消訂單。中國早前亦暫停歐洲三文魚進口，北京多間超市把三文魚下架。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1312852&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1312852%26csid%3D261_367&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4watywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=4c5146bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1312852&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:46:36.000Z","msg":"以後唔賣俾你 食屎啦"},{"pid":"5f146dd9424f5f33882d9489e730d137888691f7","tid":2068852,"uid":277339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"因為來源係紅鱒？"},{"pid":"f2ee459545ab67595360241efc8d4d10bc081ebc","tid":2068852,"uid":74622,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:47:43.000Z","msg":"咱们这么强大<br />\n全球第二大经济体<br />\n故意用广东话说后果自负的解放军<br />\n你们黄尸就不怕吗?"},{"pid":"86fa16e6765d19620ddfc78aea680ba38ec9922c","tid":2068852,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:49:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e58909636d12e560ac457196a8c0af9ed1dbb06","tid":2068852,"uid":59511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:54:18.000Z","msg":"事實證明，俾人屈唔出聲佢就更加大聲再屈多鑊"},{"pid":"99b7bccaf1aca5bb8327764c1ddcaab36d71f7b8","tid":2068852,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f91eb349c9c3b0f5ba43995fd8bce0622aad4f","tid":2068852,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a0a56d25a3e2f172548aff51875b5b08ea2812","tid":2068852,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:29:13.000Z","msg":"中共賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f